questiondata.strat-other: I use the same strategy I used to study for tests in college. I pretend like I am writing them down in my mind on a list and then I go up the list and try to remember as many as possible. In my mind I put a picture of the object next to the item on my imaginary list and then relate all of the images with each-other using a story.
